flowchart TD

    A[Admin opens Student Detail Progress Page] --> B{Choose Student Progress Feature}

    B --> C[Completed Lesson]
    B --> D[Assignment]
    B --> E[Certificate]

    %% Completed Lesson
    C --> C1[Load completed lessons]
    C1 --> C2{Any completed lessons?}
    C2 -->|No| C3[Show empty state]
    C2 -->|Yes| C4[Show completed lessons list]
    C4 --> C5{Admin clicks Reset Progress?}
    C5 -->|No| C6[Stay on completed lesson view]
    C5 -->|Yes| C7[Show confirmation dialog]
    C7 --> C8{Confirm reset?}
    C8 -->|No| C6
    C8 -->|Yes| C9[Reset lesson progress]
    C9 --> C10[Refresh completed lesson data]

    %% Assignment
    D --> D1[Load assignment table]
    D1 --> D2{Any assignment data?}
    D2 -->|No| D3[Show empty state]
    D2 -->|Yes| D4[Show assignment rows with title video status feedback]
    D4 --> D5{Choose action}
    D5 -->|Save| D6[Save assignment changes]
    D5 -->|Send Email| D7[Trigger assignment email process]
    D5 -->|Delete Video| D8[Show delete confirmation]
    D8 --> D9{Confirm delete?}
    D9 -->|No| D4
    D9 -->|Yes| D10[Delete assignment video]
    D6 --> D11[Refresh assignment table]
    D7 --> D11
    D10 --> D11

    %% Certificate
    E --> E1[Load certificate management area]
    E1 --> E2{Choose action}
    E2 -->|Generate Certificate| E3[Choose certificate type]
    E3 --> E4{Certificate Type}
    E4 -->|Bikram Yoga Certificate| E5[Generate Bikram certificate]
    E4 -->|Yoga Alliance Certification| E6[Generate Yoga Alliance certificate]
    E5 --> E7[Save certificate record]
    E6 --> E7
    E2 -->|Send Graduation Email| E8[Trigger graduation email]
    E2 -->|Recreate Certificate| E9[Generate new certificate version]
    E2 -->|Download Certificate| E10[Download certificate file]
    E2 -->|Delete Certificate| E11[Show delete confirmation]
    E11 --> E12{Confirm delete?}
    E12 -->|No| E1
    E12 -->|Yes| E13[Delete certificate]
    E7 --> E14[Refresh certificate area]
    E8 --> E14
    E9 --> E14
    E10 --> E14
    E13 --> E14